title: OHSAA state golf: Hudson's Will Kurtz wins Division I boys individual title in record fashion; Green girls team 2nd (photos, videos)
text:
Published By: Cleveland.com: Chagrin Falls - Today 
Hudson's Will Kurtz sets records on his way to the OHSAA Division I boys golf title. Green's girls team takes second overall....
